## Setting up Xi1.x online search system


You need 4 machines, or VMs.

1. Apache PHP webserver ("webserver")
2. Storage server
3. Database server
4. Computational server/compute machine

All of them can be linux boxes. This configuration is done with Ubuntu 20.04.

### configuration of the webserver
You need apache (2.4.38 or later) , PHP (7.3 or later)

    sudo apt-get install apache2 php

