### configuration of the database server
You need postGreS (9.6 or later, we also tested with 11)

    sudo apt-get install postgresql postgresl-contrib postgresql-client



For the database, you also need the definition of crosslinkers and modifications. You can download a version of our crosslinker database here 


### configuration of the computational server

You need Java (8 or later. Versions 12 or above have been seen )

    sudo apt-get install default-jre default-jdk